companyName: iShares Edge MSCI Intl Momentum Factor
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the MSCI World ex USA Momentum Index that measures the performance of international developed large- and mid-capitalization stocks exhibiting relatively higher momentum characteristics.
 The fund will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities of the index and in investments that have economic characteristics that are substantially identical to the component securities of the index. The index consists of stocks exhibiting relatively higher momentum characteristics than the traditional market capitalization-weighted parent index, the MSCI World ex USA Index.
